snippet.textDisplay:
One interpretation of the storyline could be that the "Traveller" character was once in the same position as Hassan Raheem was at the start of the track. The Traveller journeyed to this timeline but became trapped in the glitch. During his entrapment, he became acquainted with all the musicians. To escape the glitch, someone else needed to take his place. When Hassan Raheem appeared in the timeline, the Traveller became intrigued (0:56), seeing a potential successor.

The Traveller then began interacting with the musicians, working to produce the specific frequencies required to re-open the portal. This effort eventually succeeded, allowing the Traveller to enter the portal and return to his original timeline (3:04), also depicted in the track's closing moments (4:34). Hassan Raheem attempted to follow the Traveller through the portal (3:18), but he ended up getting stuck in the glitch himself, as shown in the final shot of the track (4:38).
